2. # File Permissions Lab

## Objective
Understand Linux file permissions

## Commands Used
ls -l
chmod +x mission.txt

## Observations
- Initial permissions: rw-r--r--
- After chmod: rwxr-xr-x

## Key Takeaway
Permissions determine who can read, write, or execute files
